Title: Big Shots
Plot: After a man is killed in his limousine, Greg finds that the murder victim has ties to the man he had to kill in self-defense.  The team finds that the brother is involved in this investigation and has to deal with him and his hostile mother.
GuestStars: Larry Mitchell, Bobby Hall, Jon Farless, Dheeaba Donghrer, Ari Zagaris, Ben Crowley, Aimee Garcia, Marlene Fort, Alicia Sixtos, Charley Rossman, Katie R. Chonacas, Robin Sydney, Laura Vandervoort, Victoria Presco
